    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p data-sourcepos=\"3:1-3:103\"><span>Analytics Cloud will be undergoing a scheduled maintenance on our Google Cloud SQL instances.</span><span> This maintenance is intended to improve the overall performance and security of our database infrastructure.</span></p>\n\n<p data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:19\"><strong>What to Expect:</strong></p>\n\n<ul data-sourcepos=\"7:1-7:27\">\n\t<li data-sourcepos=\"7:1-7:27\"><strong>Date:</strong><span> June 29th &amp; 30th,</span><span> 2024</span></li>\n\t<li data-sourcepos=\"8:1-8:75\"><strong>Downtime:</strong><span> We anticipate minimal downtime,</span><span> lasting only a few minutes.</span></li>\n\t<li data-sourcepos=\"9:1-9:13\"><strong>Impact:</strong><span> You may experience brief interruptions to your access to Analytics Cloud during the maintenance window for your region. There will be no interruptions in data ingestion during this time.&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p data-sourcepos=\"11:1-11:35\"><strong>Maintenance Schedule by Region:</strong></p>\n\n<ul data-sourcepos=\"13:1-13:1\">\n\t<li data-sourcepos=\"13:1-13:1\"><span>London Region:</span><span> June 29th,</span><span> 12:</span><span>00 AM UTC</span></li>\n\t<li data-sourcepos=\"14:1-14:43\"><span>Frankfurt Region:</span><span> June 29th,</span><span> 12:</span><span>00 AM UTC</span></li>\n\t<li data-sourcepos=\"15:1-15:40\"><span>Oregon Region:</span><span> June 29th,</span><span> 8:</span><span>00 AM UTC</span></li>\n\t<li data-sourcepos=\"15:1-15:40\"><span>India Region: June 29th, 1:00 PM PDT</span></li>\n\t<li data-sourcepos=\"16:1-17:0\"><span>São Paulo Region:</span><span> June 30th,</span><span> 4:</span><span>00 AM UTC</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p data-sourcepos=\"18:1-18:25\"><strong>For More Information:</strong></p>\n\n<p data-sourcepos=\"20:1-20:122\"><span>For detailed information about the type of maintenance being performed,</span><span> please refer to the Google Cloud SQL documentation:</span><span> </span><a class=\"traceable-link\" href=\"https://cloud.google.com/sql/docs/postgres/maintenance\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Cloud SQL for PostgreSQL Maintenance</a></p>\n\n<p data-sourcepos=\"22:1-22:166\"><span>We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause and appreciate your understanding.</span><span> Should you have any questions,</span><span> please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</span></p>"
      },
